# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# EduGest вҖ” Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to version control.
# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

# Supabase project URL (found in: Supabase Dashboard вҶ’ Settings вҶ’ API)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.supabase.co

# Supabase anonymous/public key (safe to expose in the browser)
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# в”Җв”Җ Optional в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

# App display name (used in page title / brand)
VITE_APP_NAME=EduGest

# Supabase Storage bucket for file uploads (create it in the dashboard)
VITE_STORAGE_BUCKET=project-wg-files

# Optional WebRTC TURN override for reliable 1:1 calls in production.
# The frontend already ships with a Metered fallback in code, which exposes those
# fallback credentials in the browser bundle. Set these variables to override it.
# Example using Metered.ca:
# VITE_TURN_URLS=turn:global.relay.metered.ca:80,turn:global.relay.metered.ca:80?transport=tcp,turn:global.relay.metered.ca:443,turns:global.relay.metered.ca:443?transport=tcp
# VITE_TURN_USERNAME=your-metered-username
# VITE_TURN_CREDENTIAL=your-metered-credential

# Optional full ICE server JSON override. This has precedence over VITE_TURN_* and
# over the embedded Metered fallback.
# Example:
# VITE_WEBRTC_ICE_SERVERS=[{"urls":"stun:stun.l.google.com:19302"},{"urls":["turn:turn.example.com:3478"],"username":"turn-user","credential":"turn-password"}]

# Base URL da API administrativa usada pelo frontend.
# Em producao no Vercel, normalmente pode ficar sem configurar e usar /api/admin.
# VITE_ADMIN_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/admin

# Supabase service role key (found in: Supabase Dashboard вҶ’ Settings вҶ’ API)
# Uso EXCLUSIVO no servidor/serverless. Nunca prefixe com VITE_.
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
